<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Signup Success</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        center {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: top;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #7c15dc;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 100px;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #f2f2f2ff;
            background-color: #6610f2;
            border: 2px solid #472ddb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #6610f2;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <center>
        <h1>Your Account Signup Successful!...</h1>
        <h3>Kindly check your registered email...</h3>
        <h3>Username and password have been sent to the registered email...</h3>
        <a href="/">Click Here To Sign In</a>
    </center>
</body>

</html>
